e Conservancy, to which the donation was made.\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5444, \"end\": 5454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8438664338185615e-16, \"text\": \"Queensland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The acquisition\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5436}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 5485, \"to\": 5496}, {\"ngram\": \"Nature Conservancy\", \"from\": 5500, \"to\": 5518}, {\"ngram\": \"the donation\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The working cattle farm is a habitat for the elusive and endangered night parrot, the vulnerable yellow-footed rock wallaby and threatened Opalton grass wren.\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5692, \"end\": 5699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opalton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Opalton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opalton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opalton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The working cattle farm\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5576}, {\"ngram\": \"a habitat\", \"from\": 5580, \"to\": 5589}, {\"ngram\": \"the elusive and endangered night parrot\", \"from\": 5594, \"to\": 5633}, {\"ngram\": \"the vulnerable yellow-footed rock wallaby\", \"from\": 5635, \"to\": 5676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This purchase is most likely the single largest donation to buy land for conservation in Australian history,\\\" James Fitzsimons from Nature Conservancy said.\", \"from\": 5713, \"to\": 5870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5803, \"end\": 5821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 5830, \"end\": 5840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vivian_Frederick_Maynard_FitzSimons\", \"score\": 0.9999999999627107, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FitzSimons\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vivian_Frederick_Maynard_FitzSimons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vivian_Frederick_Maynard_FitzSimons\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This purchase\", \"from\": 5714, \"to\": 5727}, {\"ngram\": \"the single largest donation\", \"from\": 5743, \"to\": 5770}, {\"ngram\": \"land\", \"from\": 5778, \"to\": 5782}, {\"ngram\": \"conservation\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5799}, {\"ngram\": \"Nature Conservancy\", \"from\": 5846, \"to\": 5864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government said boulder opal mining operations would be allowed to continue on 40,000 hectares of the property, but the rest of it would be converted into a national park.\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 6047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 5886}, {\"ngram\": \"boulder opal mining operations\", \"from\": 5892, \"to\": 5922}, {\"ngram\": \"40,000 hectares\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5970}, {\"ngram\": \"the property\", \"from\": 5974, \"to\": 5986}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 5992, \"to\": 6000}, {\"ngram\": \"a national park\", \"from\": 6031, \"to\": 6046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The work done so far by thenow-dumped bipartisan youth justice reform committeehas just been tabled in parliament for all to see.\", \"from\": 6049, \"to\": 6178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The work\", \"from\": 6049, \"to\": 6057}, {\"ngram\": \"thenow-dumped bipartisan youth justice reform\", \"from\": 6073, \"to\": 6118}, {\"ngram\": \"committeehas\", \"from\": 6119, \"to\": 6131}, {\"ngram\": \"parliament\", \"from\": 6152, \"to\": 6162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its release was taken from the hands of Labor and LNP MPs on the seven-person special committee, led by independent Noosa MP Sandy Bolton, after delays and lack of agreement on the contents and recommendations.\", \"from\": 6180, \"to\": 6390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6220, \"end\": 6225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0683209938254749e-39, \"text\": \"Labor\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Labor_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 6230, \"end\": 6233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1405176382306164e-36, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 6296, \"end\": 6301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Noosa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7638782862580865e-31, \"text\": \"Noosa\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Noosa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shire_of_Noosa\"}, {\"begin\": 6302, \"end\": 6304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9993216048724911, \"rank\": 0.0006788556565019475, \"text\": \"MP\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 6305, \"end\": 6317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Bolton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sandy Bolton\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Bolton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Bolton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its release\", \"from\": 6180, \"to\": 6191}, {\"ngram\": \"the hands\", \"from\": 6207, \"to\": 6216}, {\"ngram\": \"the seven-person special committee\", \"from\": 6241, \"to\": 6275}, {\"ngram\": \"delays\", \"from\": 6325, \"to\": 6331}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 6336, \"to\": 6340}, {\"ngram\": \"agreement\", \"from\": 6344, \"to\": 6353}, {\"ngram\": \"the contents\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6369}, {\"ngram\": \"recommendations\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can read the report for yourself below, and we will take a closer look at some of its details - not to mention unpack some of the claims made by MPs.\", \"from\": 6392, \"to\": 6545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the report\", \"from\": 6405, \"to\": 6415}, {\"ngram\": \"a closer look\", \"from\": 6453, \"to\": 6466}, {\"ngram\": \"its details\", \"from\": 6478, \"to\": 6489}, {\"ngram\": \"the claims\", \"from\": 6522, \"to\": 6532}, {\"ngram\": \"MPs\", \"from\": 6541, \"to\": 6544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At first glance, there are 60 recommendations with many requiring the government to do additional investigation or planning work to support longer-term change, or things the government has said it would do such as increase Childrens Court transparency.\", \"from\": 6547, \"to\": 6799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"first glance\", \"from\": 6550, \"to\": 6562}, {\"ngram\": \"60 recommendations\", \"from\": 6574, \"to\": 6592}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 6613, \"to\": 6627}, {\"ngram\": \"additional investigation\", \"from\": 6634, \"to\": 6658}, {\"ngram\": \"planning work\", \"from\": 6662, \"to\": 6675}, {\"ngram\": \"longer-term change\", \"from\": 6687, \"to\": 6705}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 6710, \"to\": 6716}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6731}, {\"ngram\": \"Childrens Court transparency\", \"from\": 6770, \"to\": 6798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the more concrete calls is to lower the threshold for serious repeat offender declarations.\", \"from\": 6801, \"to\": 6898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the more concrete calls\", \"from\": 6807, \"to\": 6830}, {\"ngram\": \"the threshold\", \"from\": 6843, \"to\": 6856}, {\"ngram\": \"serious repeat offender declarations\", \"from\": 6861, \"to\": 6897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While not making any recommendations, the report also details debate among MPs about the role of social and traditional media in the community's understanding and perception of youth crime.\", \"from\": 6900, \"to\": 7089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any recommendations\", \"from\": 6917, \"to\": 6936}, {\"ngram\": \"the report\", \"from\": 6938, \"to\": 6948}, {\"ngram\": \"MPs\", \"from\": 6975, \"to\": 6978}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 6985, \"to\": 6993}, {\"ngram\": \"social and traditional media\", \"from\": 6997, \"to\": 7025}, {\"ngram\": \"the community's understanding\", \"from\": 7029, \"to\": 7058}, {\"ngram\": \"perception\", \"from\": 7063, \"to\": 7073}, {\"ngram\": \"youth crime\", \"from\": 7077, \"to\": 7088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scientists fear time is running out to protect the Great Barrier Reef, which is enduring one of its most extensive coral bleaching events.\", \"from\": 7091, \"to\": 7229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Scientists\", \"from\": 7091, \"to\": 7101}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 7107, \"to\": 7111}, {\"ngram\": \"the Great Barrier Reef\", \"from\": 7138, \"to\": 7160}, {\"ngram\": \"its most extensive coral bleaching events\", \"from\": 7187, \"to\": 7228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The full extent of the impact is still unknown despite a \\\"gut-wrenching\\\" update yesterday that revealed almost three-quarters of the reef has been affected.\", \"from\": 7231, \"to\": 7387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The full extent\", \"from\": 7231, \"to\": 7246}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 7250, \"to\": 7260}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"gut-wrenching\\\" update\", \"from\": 7286, \"to\": 7310}, {\"ngram\": \"almost three-quarters\", \"from\": 7335, \"to\": 7356}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef\", \"from\": 7360, \"to\": 7368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reef has suffered the worst summer on record after being hit by two tropical cyclones and severe flooding plus an outbreak of coral-munching crown-of-thorns starfish.\", \"from\": 7389, \"to\": 7559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reef\", \"from\": 7389, \"to\": 7397}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst summer\", \"from\": 7411, \"to\": 7427}, {\"ngram\": \"record\", \"from\": 7431, \"to\": 7437}, {\"ngram\": \"two tropical cyclones\", \"from\": 7457, \"to\": 7478}, {\"ngram\": \"severe flooding\", \"from\": 7483, \"to\": 7498}, {\"ngram\": \"an outbreak\", \"from\": 7504, \"to\": 7515}, {\"ngram\": \"thorns\", \"from\": 7543, \"to\": 7549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has culminated in one of the reef's most widespread and severe mass coral bleaching events on record.\", \"from\": 7561, \"to\": 7667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reef's most widespread and severe mass coral bleaching events\", \"from\": 7591, \"to\": 7656}, {\"ngram\": \"record\", \"from\": 7660, \"to\": 7666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2023-24 summer update was released by the Great Barrier Reef Marine Park Authority, the Australian Institute of Marine Science and the CSIRO.\", \"from\": 7669, \"to\": 7814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2023-24 summer update\", \"from\": 7669, \"to\": 7694}, {\"ngram\": \"the Great Barrier Reef Marine Park Authority\", \"from\": 7711, \"to\": 7755}, {\"ngram\": \"the Australian Institute\", \"from\": 7757, \"to\": 7781}, {\"ngram\": \"Marine Science\", \"from\": 7785, \"to\": 7799}, {\"ngram\": \"the CSIRO\", \"from\": 7804, \"to\": 7813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It gives insight into the reef's fifth mass bleaching in eight years due to heat stress driven by climate change.\", \"from\": 7816, \"to\": 7929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"insight\", \"from\": 7825, \"to\": 7832}, {\"ngram\": \"the reef's fifth mass bleaching\", \"from\": 7838, \"to\": 7869}, {\"ngram\": \"eight years\", \"from\": 7873, \"to\": 7884}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 7897, \"to\": 7903}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 7914, \"to\": 7928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"James Cook University's Professor Terry Hughes said the shortening gap between bleaching events was a major concern, casting doubt over any subsequent full recovery.\", \"from\": 7931, \"to\": 8096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7931, \"end\": 7952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Cook_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Cook University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Cook_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Cook_University\"}, {\"begin\": 7971, \"end\": 7977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billy_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999999984847818, \"rank\": 1.2337137489630872e-09, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billy_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billy_Hughes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shortening gap\", \"from\": 7983, \"to\": 8001}, {\"ngram\": \"bleaching events\", \"from\": 8010, \"to\": 8026}, {\"ngram\": \"a major concern\", \"from\": 8031, \"to\": 8046}, {\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 8056, \"to\": 8061}, {\"ngram\": \"any subsequent full recovery\", \"from\": 8067, \"to\": 8095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have already seen back-to-back bleaching events in two consecutive years in 2016-17 and the last three events, including this one, have only been two years apart,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 8098, \"to\": 8274, \"entities\": [], \"no